<para>with all containers Armadillo-typed (arma::Mat, arma::Col, arma::uvec, etc.). Internally wraps the new Eigen-based <ref refid="classOpenOrbitalOptimizer_1_1SCFSolver" kindref="compound">OpenOrbitalOptimizer::SCFSolver&lt;Tbase, IsComplex&gt;</ref>, with Armadillo&lt;-&gt; Eigen conversion at the <ref refid="classOpenOrbitalOptimizer_1_1SCFSolver" kindref="compound">SCFSolver</ref> boundary. The conversions are memcpy-cost (column-major to column-major) and the Fock-builder callback is bridged transparently.</para>
<para>Including this header pulls in &lt;armadillo&gt;. The core library itself remains Armadillo-free; only consumers who include this header pay the Armadillo dependency. Only the four legacy scalar pairs are supported: (float,float), (double,double), (std::complex&lt;float&gt;,float), (std::complex&lt;double&gt;,double). </para>
